---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	lang="en"
	title="Cookies — Gandía, summer 2026"
	description="About the cookies on this site. Short version: we don't use any for tracking or advertising. The only cookies that may be set are technical ones used by Netlify to serve the site."
	otherLangHref="/es/cookies/"
	otherLangLabel="Español"
>
	<p class="eyebrow">Cookies</p>
	<h1>About our <span class="accent">cookies</span></h1>
	<p class="tagline">
		Short version: we don't use any for tracking or advertising.
	</p>

	<h2>What's actually set</h2>
	<p>
		The site uses <strong>no analytics cookies, no advertising cookies and no third-party trackers</strong>. No Google Analytics, no Facebook Pixel, no marketing tags.
	</p>
	<p>
		The only cookies you may encounter are <strong>technical cookies</strong> set by <a href="https://www.netlify.com/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Netlify</a>, the platform that hosts the site, for security and load balancing. They're required to deliver the site to your browser and don't track you across other sites.
	</p>

	<h2>If you'd rather opt out</h2>
	<p>
		Block them in your browser's settings or use private/incognito mode. The site will still work normally.
	</p>

	<p class="signoff">Questions? <a href="/contact/">Get in touch.</a></p>

	<style>
		h2 {
			font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
			font-size: 1.4rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			margin: 2.2rem 0 0.7rem;
			letter-spacing: -0.01em;
			color: var(--ink);
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
